							<text>"The most known battle in Rebel history was the Battle of Node 17, often referred to as the Last Stand. The outcome of Node 17 has never been repeated except for Universe 0, the origins of multiverse travelers. Though the Federation was successful in defeating the Rebels, their celebration would not last for long after the Rebels discovered the mysterious Multiverse technology."</text>
							<modifyPursuit amount="1"/>
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Continue...</text>
								<event>
									<text>"We owe our collective thanks to the brave heroes who have provided the other Rebels across the realities the chance to bring a better future to their galaxy. This concludes the retelling. Accept this complementary augment and supplies for taking the time to educate yourself."</text>
									<autoReward level="HIGH">standard</autoReward>
									<augment name="RANDOM"/>
								</event>
							</choice>
						</event>
					</choice>
					<choice hidden="true">
						<text>Stop listening.</text>
						<event>
							<text>Almost the second you mute the Auto-ship, its weapons activate and it attacks!</text>
							<ship hostile="true"/> 
							<choice hidden="true">
								<text>Continue...</text>
