<event name="FLAGSHIP_CONSTRUCTION_DONE">
	<text>You know with an infinite amount of potential realities there is thousands more Flagships out there, but without this one at least one more reality has been saved. It's a major victory, and there's countless scrap for you to collect, and even the blueprints of a Rebel cruiser left unprotected! Cautious of reinforcements arriving, you take as much as you can and leave. The Fleet will likely be too distracted dealing with this loss to follow you.</text>
